I used CloudWatch mainly for monitoring, alerting, and troubleshooting production issues.
I worked with metrics, logs, alarms, and dashboards to ensure application availability and performance.

1. Monitoring EC2 & Application Health
I monitored EC2 CPU, memory (via custom metrics), disk usage
Created CloudWatch Alarms:
CPU > 70% → trigger alert
Status check failed → immediate alert
Integrated alarms with SNS to notify team

I configured CloudWatch alarms for EC2 metrics and integrated them 
with SNS to send alerts when thresholds were breached.
